dc_description_s: This data layer represents municipalities for Green County, Wisconsin in 2015. [Features were derived from a variety of sources including deeds, descriptions, subdivision maps, certified survey maps, easements, and right of way maps. These source materials were of varying scale and date. This coverage provides a representation of the geometry and topology of tax parcels within the County, and is suitable as a reference layer within the County's GIS.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For additional information, please see original license/data sharing agreement where applicable. Best known date is 5/10/2015. For complete metadata documentation and online dataset download, please visit http://www.co.green.wi.gov/localgov_departments_details.asp?deptid=115&locid=148.
